data.description: Welcome to this inviting ranch-style home that exudes comfort and space. Nestled on two generously sized lots, this property offers ample room for various activities and relaxation.Key Features:Master Bedroom & Second Bedroom with Shower: Enjoy the convenience of a master bedroom alongside a second bedroom equipped with a shower, ensuring both comfort and functionality.Eight Rooms in Total: With a layout featuring eight rooms, this property provides versatility and space for various purposes.Office Space: Perfect for those who work from home or need a dedicated workspace.Spare Room: Offering flexibility for guests or as an additional relaxation area.Sunroom: Embrace natural light and relaxation in this charming sunlit space, ideal for leisure and year-round enjoyment.The house is thoughtfully designed to accommodate various lifestyles, whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or an ideal place for entertaining. The two lots not only offer plenty of outdoor space but also provide potential for landscaping, gardening, or any outdoor activities.  There's a detached 2 car garage on the back lot with a loft above for extra storage or useful as a private work space. Enjoy the convenience of a robot lawn mowing system pre-programmed for the entire yard. There's also a storage shed on the lot.   Included with your yearly POA fee is access to Lake Tansi's 5 beautiful lakes, brand new indoor swimming pool and the brand new outdoor swimming pool. Don't miss the opportunity to make this versatile and spacious ranch-style house your new home!
